{"tid":170274,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美劇翻拍《死亡筆記本》風格大變　超帥夜神月驚豔網友","createTime":"2017-03-24T15:38:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-24T17:59:43.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5f7154846a153946526a42c2b6498e8df76749ea","tid":170274,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T15:38:52.000Z","msg":"Netflix 於今（3/23）日宣佈旗下原創電影《死亡筆記本》將於 8 月 25 日全球獨家首映。 本片由擅長黑色幽默及恐怖題材的獨立製片導演亞當・溫高德執導，並且在電影版注入更多不同的成人元素，將原作的世界觀與故事分享給全世界，製片 Roy Lee 也表示，這部電影完全是為成人而設的，也請觀眾拭目以待。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4TciAxwAsJQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4TciAxwAsJQ&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=8460d0f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4TciAxwAsJQ</a><br />\n<br />\n《死亡筆記本》主要是在描述一名高中生意外得到一本擁有超自然能力的筆記本，只要寫上任何人的名字並想著那人的長相，對方就會因此喪命。沈醉於這種神一般的能力，這名青年決定開始殺害一切他覺得不配活在世上的人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2415/e2415051.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2415%2Fe2415051.jpg&h=78285c2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這部改編自大場鶇和小畑健合著的著名漫畫，不僅在日本陸續改編成動畫、影集、電影及舞台劇，本次由 Netflix 所推出的電影版將邀請演員納特・沃爾夫（《紙上城市》）、瑪格麗特・庫利（《末世餘生》）、斯・史坦費爾德（《逃出絕命鎮》）、保羅・中內（《神鬼奇航3：世界的盡頭》）、希亞・溫漢（《瞞天大佈局》）和威廉‧達佛（《蜘蛛人》）⋯⋯等知名演員擔綱演出。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2415/e2415050.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2415%2Fe2415050.jpg&h=b4825cb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而飾演男女主角的納特・沃爾夫（夜神月）及瑪格麗特・庫利（彌海砂），其實現實中也曾經交往過兩年（於 2014 年分手），昔日情侶如今於大螢幕再續前緣，兩人演技將擦出何種火花，也讓不少粉絲觀眾期待。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://game.ettoday.net/article/891605.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgame.ettoday.net%2Farticle%2F891605.htm&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=d96d2d5e\" target=\"_blank\">http://game.ettoday.net/article/891605.htm</a>"},{"pid":"fe842d1bd189ac60bc42d20bd9e507f7fa1f6ec6","tid":170274,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T15:44:04.000Z","msg":"超帥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3925f5f6d3b6be52fabae7d64b29b4cfddce9941","tid":170274,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T15:45:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2415/e2415051.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2415%2Fe2415051.jpg&h=78285c2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n左邊果個唔撚係流克下話?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌, 你求其搵個鐵血戰士或者異形當係流克都好過搵個真人黎扮流克"},{"pid":"2b7c8912096f15e29ab4179e211f3cdc6ac578a4","tid":170274,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T15:46:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2415/e2415051.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2415%2Fe2415051.jpg&h=78285c2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n左邊果個唔撚係流克下話?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌, 你求其搵個鐵血戰士或者異形當係流克都好過搵個真人黎扮流克</blockquote><br />\n睇坐姿都好明顯呀...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"724137ae9651d27c36f0e9875600b8a3b018e12a","tid":170274,"uid":5322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T15:50:13.000Z","msg":"好柒...<br />\n本death note變左成本黃頁咁厚，仲有啲九唔搭八雕花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7220efde09892c9e031ffbff10f8e9bf1a823fc4","tid":170274,"uid":46894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T15:51:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2415/e2415051.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2415%2Fe2415051.jpg&h=78285c2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n左邊果個唔撚係流克下話?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌